rows.label: qst105604_msg001
rows.name:
反乱が起きた
反乱分子は今までアデルの末裔だと
黙っていたことに対して憤慨している

rows.label: qst105604_msg002
rows.name:
すまないが　反乱分子を
排除してきてもらえないだろうか

rows.label: qst105604_msg0001
rows.name: What's going on?!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0002
rows.name: Your Highness...!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0003
rows.name:
Some of our men who heard the
rumors about his Majesty and Adel
have turned on us!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0004
rows.name: What?!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0005
rows.name:
They're saying that they're going to
take up arms against the king because
he hid the truth from them!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0006
rows.name: Crap, I was worried this might happen!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0007
rows.name: Better get to it, my Prince!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0008
rows.name: What are we looking at?

rows.label: qst105604_msg0009
rows.name:
The soldiers who planned the coup
are starting skirmishes all over the
castle!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0010
rows.name:
Tell all units to suppress the enemy
uprising and secure the area, ASAP!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0011
rows.name: Understood, Your Highness!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0012
rows.name: All right, time to join the fray!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0013
rows.name:
Sorry about this, Saika.
Never thought I'd be getting you roped
you up in personal troubles.

rows.label: qst105604_msg0014
rows.name:
Hey, I'm your Blade. Your burden
is my burden, remember. Half of
this is my responsibility.

rows.label: qst105604_msg0015
rows.name: Still...

rows.label: qst105604_msg0016
rows.name:
You're clearly much stronger than me.
I reckon we should split it 70:30.

rows.label: qst105604_msg0017
rows.name:
Wow.
All right, fine, have it your way!

rows.label: qst105604_msg0018
rows.name:
That's my Saika! Come on then,
we've got a rebellion to quash!
